                                </svg>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="fw-bold">Legal Hold - Litigation</div>
                        <div class="fs-xs text-muted">Data under legal hold - do not delete</div>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <span class="fw-bold">Indefinite</span>
                    </td>
